          "text": "百日内还有那血光灾星。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二不可三皇庙求雨祈神。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四不可清幽观结拜赵京。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "六不可黄叶寺惹祸生嗔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八不可鱼池内射妖逞能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十不可高平关将妹许婚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到后来才知我苗顺卦灵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一不可董家桥自逞本领"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三不可华山上下棋争论"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "五不可宿古庙恐遭迷阵"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "七不可归故里盘查严紧"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "九不可上燕京刺杀刘主"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我算你十件事件件有准"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苗先生他把我未来算定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只说得赵玄郎二目圆睁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再算我到何日大运亨通？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走向前施一礼还要求问"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我算你四十岁才交大运，"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到陈桥戴冕旒南面称尊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苗先生你说话需要谨慎，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这件事犯王法不可看轻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪有个荫子孙擅坐朝廷？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那时节你就是开国元勋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽则是我祖父为官清正"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵玄郎若还有天子福分"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我在那江湖上四路访问，"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只等到八月中相会汴京。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "洒金桥算八卦半疑半信，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不知到后来灵也不灵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "普天下捉拿我画影图形。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在他乡落圈套有翅难腾。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵匡胤下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苗顺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "几句话说得他无言可问，"
        }
